    "desc": "We transform highly specialised engineering knowledge into practical and productive solutions for a number of industries. ",
    "navbar": "About us\nContact\nsearch\nChoose language",
    "text": "You control your data\nWe and our partners use technologies, including cookies, to collect, store and use personal information about:\nyour chosen preferences with an aim to customising the website so that you get a better user experience.\nyour visits to the website to understand how visitors interact with the website, as well as pass on this information to our partners with regard to making the page more intuitive, provide you with personalised content and prepare market analysis.\nyour activity on the website and your IP address with an aim at targeting our marketing.\nBy clicking on 'Accept all' you give consent for all of these purposes. You can also choose to indicate which specific purposes you want to consent to by using the buttons next to the purpose, and then press 'Accept selected'. You can withdraw your consent at any time via the link at the bottom of the website.\nRead more about the use of cookies on our website by clicking 'Show details' and about our processing of personal data here.\nAbout cookies\nDECLINE ALL\nACCEPT ALL\nShow details\nStrictly necessary\nNecessary cookies help make a website usable by enabling basic functions like page navigation and access to secure areas of the website. The website cannot function properly without these cookies.\nFunctional\nWe collect information about your preferred setting and behaviour on the website. We do that to show you the best version of our website according to your preferences.\nStatistical\nWe collect data on how you interact with the website including how often you visit the website, and which pages you look at. We do this in order to optimise the design, usability and strengthen the efficiency of the website. In addition, we use the data to provide you with personalised content and to prepare market analysis.\nMarketing\nMarketing cookies are used to track visitors across websites. The intention is to deliver content that is relevant and engaging for the individual user.\nUnclassified\nWe are in the process of classifying unclassified cookies together with the providers of the individual cookies.\nStrictly necessary\nFunctional\nStatistical\nMarketing\n\n\n\nAbout us\nContact\nsearch\nChoose language\nSERVICES\nTESTING FACILITIES\nKEY TOPICS\nINDUSTRIES\nINNOVATION\nKNOWLEDGE AND COURSES\nNEWS\nDigital twin facilitates more intelligent decision-making at production facility\nsearch\nDigitalisation - we drive innovation and technological change\nGreen transition - we develop technology to accelerate the green transition\nHealth - we contribute to improving human health and safety",
